Subject: Re: [VB] stuck motor?

Remove the rocker shafts from the cylinder heads.
Place a ruler across the valve stems.

Also check the carb throat for a missing squirter.
If it's gone, turn that engine upside down and shake it
out the spark plug hole. Or use a brass magnet:)
Dave \X/

